    role: "Fossil collector and preparator",
    oneLineHook: "She found the creatures; the men got the credit.",
    knownFor: "Discovered the first complete ichthyosaur, first plesiosaur, and first British pterosaur - the foundational specimens that made Jurassic marine reptiles visible to science.",
