    knownFor: "Identified the iridium anomaly at the Cretaceous-Palaeogene boundary in 1980, providing the first physical evidence for a major asteroid impact at the end of the Cretaceous - and igniting the debate that eventually established the impact hypothesis for the mass extinction.",
